00:43:23.100 --> 00:43:25.603
PICTURES HE TOOK OF
MALCOLM IN AN APARTMENT

00:43:26.103 --> 00:43:28.606
WITH JAPANESE PEOPLE
SITTING NEXT TO HIM.

