HE SHOOK HANDS WITH -- THE
PLACE WAS PACKED, BUT

00:44:00.137 --> 00:44:02.640
THOSE OF NEAR ENOUGH WHO
COULD SHAKE HANDS WITH

00:44:02.640 --> 00:44:06.644
HIM, THEY NOTICED THAT HE
WAS AS WARM TO WHITES AS

00:44:06.644 --> 00:44:07.645
HE WAS TO BLACKS.

