HE WAS JUST WONDERFUL TO
EVERYBODY WHO WAS THERE.

00:44:11.148 --> 00:44:12.650
AND WHAT DID YOU THINK?

00:44:12.650 --> 00:44:15.653
OH, I MEAN [LAUGHS] WE
